{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"377efc56-9790-4faf-9317-816856a77fa9","content":"The project path doesn't exist in my environment, but here's exactly what you need to configure:\n\n### 1. `.csproj` — Add dotnet tool + NuGet properties\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <PackAsTool>true</PackAsTool>\n  <ToolCommandName>my-mcp-server</ToolCommandName>\n\n  <!-- NuGet metadata -->\n  <PackageId>MyMcpServer</PackageId>\n  <Version>1.0.0</Version>\n  <Authors>YourName</Authors>\n  <Description>An MCP server for ...</Description>\n  <PackageLicenseExpression>MIT</PackageLicenseExpression>\n  <PackageProjectUrl>https://github.com/you/MyMcpServer</PackageProjectUrl>\n  <RepositoryUrl>https://github.com/you/MyMcpServer</RepositoryUrl>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\n**Key properties:**\n- **`PackAsTool`** — marks this as a .NET tool (required)\n- **`ToolCommandName`** — the CLI command users run (e.g., `my-mcp-server`)\n- The `OutputType` must be `Exe` (should already be the case for a stdio server)\n\n### 2. Pack & Publish\n\n```bash\n# Create the .nupkg\ndotnet pack -c Release\n\n# Push to NuGet.org (get API key from https://www.nuget.org/account/apikeys)\ndotnet nuget push bin/Release/MyMcpServer.1.0.0.nupkg \\\n  --api-key YOUR_API_KEY \\\n  --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n```\n\n### 3. Users install & run it\n\n```bash\ndotnet tool install -g MyMcpServer\nmy-mcp-server            # runs via stdio\n```\n\n### Tips\n- Use `<PackageReadmeFile>` to bundle a `README.md` in the package\n- Use `<PackageIcon>` for a logo on nuget.org\n- Set `<IsPackable>true</IsPackable>` if your build warns about packing\n- For CI, store the API key as a secret and publish from your pipeline","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"0591cd4e-a4ba-44b4-a579-263edbc2642a","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The project doesn't exist yet. The user is asking for guidance on what they need to configure. Let me provide them with the necessary configuration steps for publishing a C# MCP server as a dotnet tool to NuGet.org.","outputTokens":611,"requestId":"3849:3E4B47:6D88EAE:75F761B:6A03D094"},"id":"b0dcc7d0-a8f2-4cfe-8770-86671a6ca8a4","timestamp":"2026-05-13T01:15:14.741Z","parentId":"ee42caa7-8024-426e-a48e-7228cd43ec73"}
